      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that slips between gears. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches on the wheel wells and several large dents, while the interior has torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal candidate for a dedicated mechanic looking for a project or for someone needing a donor vehicle for parts.",
