    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it's a total gem! This beauty is in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014spotless inside and out, not a single scratch to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. You\u2019ve really got to see it in person to believe how pristine it is! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
